      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b Are you looking for a ride that\u2019s basically brand new? This car is in absolute mint condition\u2014seriously, it looks and smells like it just left the showroom! It\u2019s been pampered its whole life, kept in a garage, and there isn't a single scratch or dent to be found. It drives like a total dream and is ready for its next adventure. You really have to see it in person to believe how pristine it is! Come check it out and fall in love! \u2728",
