    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade E46 M3, featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six equipped with individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing. This specimen boasts a precise Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and a factory-calibrated M-Variable limited-slip differential. The chassis is structurally flawless, featuring proactive subframe reinforcement and refreshed bushings to maintain original torsional rigidity. With a crisp 8,000 RPM redline and an impeccable aesthetic, this vehicle is a turnkey masterpiece for the performance purist.",
