    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional vehicle that can only be described as a showroom-quality time capsule. This car has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled environment, resulting in an exterior with a deep, mirror-like luster and absolutely zero swirl marks, chips, or imperfections. Inside, the cabin remains in factory-fresh condition; the premium leather upholstery is supple and free of any wear or creasing, and the interior still retains that distinct new-car aroma. Every electronic component, button, and switch functions with the crisp precision of the day it left the assembly line. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, backed by a comprehensive, single-owner service history performed exclusively at authorized dealerships. It has never seen rain or snow, and the undercarriage is as clean as the bodywork. This is a rare opportunity for a discerning collector or enthusiast to own a flawless example of automotive excellence.",
      "price": 44900.0,
