    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b I am so excited to show you this absolute gem! It has been my pride and joy, and I\u2019ve taken such good care of it that it honestly looks and feels brand new. It\u2019s in pristine condition inside and out\u2014seriously, you won't find a single flaw. If you're looking for a ride that's been pampered and is ready for a new home, this is the one for you! Come say hi and take it for a spin! \u2728",
      "price": 46500.0,
